name: Hoarder Alert
description:
Congratulations if you own this token 🎉🎉🎉🎉

If you're collecting multiple editions of the same token in an effort to drain the availability so you can sell them and make a profit, then you are probably missing the point of #OBJKT4OBJKT and what you're doing is depriving people who genuinely like my pieces but for one reason or another they are only able to get them on OBJKT4OBJKT.

Please consider my only warning about this behaviour. Keep 2 tokens. One to sell, and one to keep if you like my art. Return the remaining tokens to me so I can put them back on the market so other people have a chance to get them.

Its very easy to identify accounts you interact with. So sending tokens or currency to other wallets doesn't really give you much anonymity.

Appreciate yout time! Enjoy
